divs: Sighting DetailsI was in the basement at home and the door was opened to outside. I saw a disc type ufo in the back yard and a pink and a yellow alien. Then a green alien, the Roswell type, came inside the basement and walked over to me and touched my arm. I had a lot of pain and blacked out for a minute. When I came to the alien was gone and so was the spaceship.
trends: There have been 11 other sightings in Portsmouth
There were no other sightings in Portsmouth on or around July 15th 1984
Summary: I saw a silver ufo in my back yard and a green alien like the Roswell kind came in and touched my arm.
